{"title":"Assos goes to the moon and back, shows love with the Interstellar Capsule","link":"https://www.cyclingtips.com/2023/03/assos-interstellar-jersey/","date":1680183584000,"content":"<figure><img src=\"https://cdn.cyclingtips.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/AssosInterstellarCapsule_allcolorways.jpg?width=1200\" alt=\"Assos goes to the moon and back, shows love with the Interstellar Capsule\" /></figure><p><a href=\"https://www.cyclingtips.com/tag/assos/\" target=\"_blank\"><span>Assos</span></a><span> has announced its latest collection, dubbed the Assos Interstellar Capsule. Each garment takes an existing jersey or short and applies “graphics inspired by the unnatural surfaces, shapes, and colors of the lunar world.“</span></p>\n<p><span>The Interstellar Capsule is based on four jerseys. Men’s-specific cuts are based on the Equipe RS and Mille GT jerseys for an aggressive, second-skin-style fit and a club-style fit accordingly. Women’s-specific cuts are available courtesy of the Dyora RS and Uma GT jerseys.</span></p>\n<figure><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://cdn.cyclingtips.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/AssosInterstellarCapsule_allcolorways2-1340x893.jpg?width=730\" alt=\"AssosInterstellarCapsule_allcolorways2\" width=\"1340\" height=\"893\" /><figcaption><span>There are six colorways available between the four men’s and women’s jerseys. (Photo: Assos)</span></figcaption></figure>\n<p><b>Read more:</b> <a href=\"https://www.cyclingtips.com/2023/03/mosaic-rt-1-itr-titanium/\" target=\"_blank\"><span>Mosaic launches the RT-1 ITR, adds a bit of thickness to their titanium road bike</span></a></p>\n<p>Both the men’s and women’s-specific Interstellar jerseys feature two separate collections. The race jerseys (Equipe RS and Dyora RS) come in “exclusive 3D Space Silver graphics.” The second collection of everyday jerseys (Mille GT and Uma GT) feature their “Lunarscape” colorways in Moon Sand, Titan Green, and Cosmic Rosé.</p>\n<p>And while there’s no mention of it, we think the best way to get that Interstellar look is by using the <a href=\"https://www.assos.com/us/zegho-g2-interceptor-black-186160.html\" target=\"_blank\">Assos Zegho G2 sunglasses</a>. Just trust us on that one.</p>\n<p><span>Jerseys are available now on </span><a href=\"https://www.assos.com/us/\" target=\"_blank\"><span>assos.com</span></a><span>. </span></p>\n<figure><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://cdn.cyclingtips.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/AssosInterstellarCapsule_lifestyle2.jpg?width=730\" alt=\"AssosInterstellarCapsule_lifestyle2\" width=\"1000\" height=\"1500\" /><figcaption><span>Pro tip for the future:. If you want to truly look interstellar, the Assos Zegho G2 glasses are a non-negotiable. (Image: Assos)</span></figcaption></figure>\n<figure><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://cdn.cyclingtips.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/AssosInterstellarCapsule_lifestyle1.jpg?width=730\" alt=\"AssosInterstellarCapsule_lifestyle1\" width=\"2953\" height=\"1969\" /><figcaption><span>The Dyora RS women’s jersey and Equipe RS men’s jersey in ‘Space Silver.’ (Image: Assos)</span></figcaption></figure>\n<figure><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://cdn.cyclingtips.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/EQUIPE-RS-Jersey-S9-TARGA-Lunar-Camou_fronte-1340x1707.jpg?width=730\" alt=\"EQUIPE RS Jersey S9 TARGA Lunar Camou_fronte\" width=\"1340\" height=\"1707\" /><figcaption><span>An Equipe RS Jersey in “Space Silver.” (Image: Assos)</span></figcaption></figure>\n<figure><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://cdn.cyclingtips.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/MILLE-GT-Jersey-C2-EVO-Moon-Sand-front-1340x1773.jpg?width=730\" alt=\"MILLE GT Jersey C2 EVO Moon Sand front\" width=\"1340\" height=\"1773\" /><figcaption><span>A Mille GT Jersey in “Moon Sand.” (Image: Assos)</span></figcaption></figure>\n<figure><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://cdn.cyclingtips.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/MILLE-GT-Jersey-C2-EVO-Titan-Green-fronte-1340x1844.jpg?width=730\" alt=\"MILLE GT Jersey C2 EVO Titan Green fronte\" width=\"1340\" height=\"1844\" /><figcaption><span>A Mille GT Jersey in “Titan Green.” (Image: Assos)</span></figcaption></figure>\n<figure><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://cdn.cyclingtips.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/DYORA-RS-Jersey-S9-TARGA-Lunar-Camou_fronte-1340x1892.jpg?width=730\" alt=\"DYORA RS Jersey S9 TARGA Lunar Camou_fronte\" width=\"1340\" height=\"1892\" /><figcaption><span>A Dyora RS Jersey in “Space Silver.” (Image: Assos)</span></figcaption></figure>\n<figure><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://cdn.cyclingtips.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/UMA-GT-Jersey-C2-EVO-Cosmic-Rose-fronte-1340x1876.jpg?width=730\" alt=\"UMA GT Jersey C2 EVO Cosmic Rose fronte\" width=\"1340\" height=\"1876\" /><figcaption><span>An Uma GT in “Cosmic Rose.” (Image: Assos)</span></figcaption></figure>\n<figure><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://cdn.cyclingtips.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/UMA-GT-Jersey-C2-EVO-Moon-Sand-fronte-1340x1938.jpg?width=730\" alt=\"UMA GT Jersey C2 EVO Moon Sand fronte\" width=\"1340\" height=\"1938\" /><figcaption><span>An Uma GT in “Moon Sand.” (Image: Assos)</span></figcaption></figure>","author":"Alvin Holbrook","siteTitle":"CyclingTips","siteHash":"30feca30fb3902119bf2da6559e7337232527b61c9abe0a00f5d7543c6aa6c84","entryHash":"d597f445b33aed87e21f64964bd089d9d2a2523353f68a8565d6c1d2e4b46007","category":"Cycling"}